<div style="background-color:rgba(43, 24, 2, 0.7); color: white; margin:1em; padding:5px 10px; border:2px solid #705232; border-radius: 3px">
<br><center><span style="font-family:Cormorant Upright;font-size:15px;">In the dwindling light, the crickets sing,</span></center>
<br><center><span style="font-family:Cormorant Upright;font-size:15px;">Their symphony of an evening ring.</span></center>
<br><center><span style="font-family:Cormorant Upright;font-size:15px;">Amidst the whispers of the breeze,</span></center>
<br><center><span style="font-family:Cormorant Upright;font-size:15px;">Their gentle song wisps through the trees.</span></center>

<br><center><span style="font-family:Cormorant Upright;font-size:15px;">The chirps are a lullaby so sweet,</span></center>
<br><center><span style="font-family:Cormorant Upright;font-size:15px;">A gentle hum, a soft heartbeat.</span></center>
<br><center><span style="font-family:Cormorant Upright;font-size:15px;">As the night begins to fall,</span></center>
<br><center><span style="font-family:Cormorant Upright;font-size:15px;">The cricket tunes begin to stall.</span></center>

<br><center><span style="font-family:Cormorant Upright;font-size:15px;">For in the fading light's embrace,</span></center>
<br><center><span style="font-family:Cormorant Upright;font-size:15px;">It's time for all to find their place.</span></center>
<br><center><span style="font-family:Cormorant Upright;font-size:15px;">To bid farewell to the shadow's roam,</span></center>
<br><center><span style="font-family:Cormorant Upright;font-size:15px;">And journey wayward back to home.</span></center>
<br><center><span style="font-family:Cormorant Upright;font-size:15px;">Come back home, darling.</span></center>
</div>
